s we can foresee more inicidents like this one are going to happen in the near future if nothing is done to stop police brutality. Thanks a lot for your time!<br />\n<br />\nA group of concerned Hong Kongers"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:22:53.000Z","msg":"Done!!!!!<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LqRStJU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLqRStJU.png&h=bcc95174&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc96ad3bcb9fbb74e7355befb2dd853260d82f22","tid":1408890,"uid":262346,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:24:40.000Z","msg":"有post 話要send 俾emma watson 知咩事<br />\n<br />\n佢仲send 埋圖<br />\n<br />\n支持樓主出去屌柒佢<br />\n<br />\n按樓主講法Emma watson想二次傷害女事主"},{"pid":"6edab2c021be7779c899f33a65f9e6c0761de1d7","tid":1408890,"uid":257315,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6e9e3bee63cc315be1e49b247c6c3b9d070a178c","tid":1408890,"uid":67786,"like":4,"dislike":41,"score":-37,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:42:08.000Z","msg":"想睇？有冇片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:36:52.000Z","msg":"有啊 無碼添 不過段片主角係你老母"},{"pid":"03354e113fcd5eec849746c4c67d592629d689f1","tid":1408890,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"fd7def848d89dbef67ac4769aae3b13150ea9d0c","tid":1408890,"uid":92376,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:41:05.000Z","msg":"可想而知班淫警平時睇幾多av<br />\n除人條褲可以咁純熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女義士真係要多加小心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:39:59.000Z","msg":"躝啦五毛"},{"pid":"d0045dcf9e6dfc0c379b2639e85c73461f1eea26","tid":1408890,"uid